casebody.data:
No. 10-291. John Tyler Clemons, et al., Appellants v. Department of Commerce, et al. 562 U.S. 1105, 131 S. Ct. 821,

178 L. Ed. 2d 552,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 9702. December 13, 2010.

On appeal from the United States District Court for the Northern District of Mississippi. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to United States District Court for the Northern District of Mississippi with instructions to dismiss the complaint for lack of jurisdiction.

Same case below, 710 F. Supp. 2d 570.
